#Summary of analysis of r_project_data_csv Chrome dataset

Insights: 1. Senior roles earn significantly more than junior and mid-level positions. 2. Non-remote roles in high-cost cities offer higher salaries (e.g., SF, NY). 3. Remote salaries are competitive but often lower than in-office roles, depending on company location. 4. Location-based salary variations are significant in large cities but less pronounced for remote work.

Outcome: 1. Team Fully Built by Q4 2. Total Salary Budget: $1.56 million 3. Expected ROI Growth: 50-100% in Year 2 4. Remote Work Savings: 10-15% on Salaries
